import React, { useEffect } from 'react'; import './conta.css'; const Conta = ({sidebarExpandido}) => { useEffect(() => { const forms = document.querySelectorAll('.needs-validation'); const handleFormSubmit = (event) => { const form = event.target; if (!form.checkValidity()) { event.preventDefault(); event.stopPropagation(); } form.classList.add('was-validated'); }; Array.from(forms).forEach(form => { form.addEventListener('submit', handleFormSubmit, false); }); return () => { Array.from(forms).forEach(form => { form.removeEventListener('submit', handleFormSubmit, false); }); }; }, []); return (
